            "text": "that we adopt for the semantic modelling of sentences . <S>\r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "The network uses Dynamic k-Max Pooling , a global pooling operation over linear sequences . <S>\r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "The network handles input sentences of varying length \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
