            "text": "that is capable of explicitly capturing short and long-range relations . <S>\r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "The network does not rely on a parse tree \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 11,
            "text": "and is easily applicable to any language . <S>\r",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
